metadata.name: Summer vacation of girls in Incrid
metadata.description:
Girls belonging to Incrid taking a vacation at the beach in summer.
The girls usually hold guns, but today they are crazy about playing in the water.
One piece that I tried to put such a record.


夏の海で休暇をとるインクリッド所属の少女たち。
普段は銃を手に取る少女たちだが今日ばかりは水遊びに夢中です。
そんな記録をおさめようとした１枚。
